            <div type="translation">
                <p>Behold, the Virgin (will conceive and give birth to a son, and they will call him Emmanuel).</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is from Isaiah 7:14 and refers to Christ's conception and birth; the text reappears in Matthew 1:23.</p>
